utline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">　　</strong></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\">为了尽可能的减少拱北隧道对口岸的影响，工程人员采用了管幕超前支护的施工方法，所谓的管幕是指由多根顶管组成的环形支护体系，拱北隧道共布置了36根这样的顶管，每根顶管直径长1.62米，平均长度为255米。</span></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: left;\"><section data-bcless=\"darken\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://u.hizh.cn/u/cms/www/201702/280844292t19.jpg\" title=\"12.jpg\" height=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseli